    },
    {
      "id": "aa95f89f22d1fef061b8f273109338769f22a3d1",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 443,
        "name": "Andrew Perepechko",
        "email": "andrew.perepechko@hpe.com",
        "username": "panda"
      },
      "date": "2016-06-17 06:50:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAs I explained in LU-8284, this test case cannot be integrated with the fix itself, because it would require sleeping under spinlock or something similar, and I'm not requesting landing for it. It is supposed for demonstration purpose only. \n\nThere are a few assumptions in the test which worked for me on my local test system and our automated system, e.g. that the first MiB gets written on the OSS earlier than the second MiB, but they did not seem to work for your system. I'm going to improve the test. Unfortunately, there are no dk logs for the \"successful\" run.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
