      "date": "2016-06-17 19:50:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-53vm1 for custom received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/b2b4f8b4-34c4-11e6-acf3-5254006e85c2). Ran 3 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
